### Initialize MCP Session
POST http://localhost:5000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": { "name": "test-client", "version": "1.0" }
  },
  "id": 1
}

